title: [Kragnek-Dzu, Crater Plaza]
description: Dominating the central gathering area of Kragnek Dzu, a magnificent fountain towers over a masterfully constructed concave plaza.  Water bubbles and splashes between colorful, chromatic glaes fragments in a wide carved stone basin that surrounds the fountain's centerpiece, a massive teardrop of pure white glaes artistically formed as if plummeting into the basin just above the water's surface.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
